S3 Encryption:
==============

Encryption:
============

    In Transit:
        SSL/TLS
    

    At Rest:
    ---------

        * Client Side
        * Server side
            using SSE - S3
            using SSE - KMS
            SSE - Customer Provided Keys
        * Control access to buckets using Bucket Policies and Bucket ACL
        * By Default S3 buckets are private and all objects stored inside it are private.